  "Description": {
    "English": "Convenient and optimized power storage unit. Used in a wide variety of <span class=\"name name-commodity\">defensive</span> and <span class=\"name name-commodity\">hazard protection</span> systems.<br> <br>Constructed by fusing <span class=\"name name-earth\">Ferrite Dust</span> with underground <span class=\"name name-technology\">Cobalt</span>. Frequently found ready-made in cylindrical metal containers.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "方便、有效的能量存储单元在<span class=\"name name-commodity\">防御系统</span>和<span class=\"name name-commodity\">危险防护系统</span>中有广泛的应用。<br> <br>可由<span class=\"name name-earth\">铁氧体粉末</span>和地下开采出的<span class=\"name name-technology\">钴</span>化合后制得。经常能在圆柱形金属容器中找到成品。",
    "TencentChinese": "方便、有效的能量存储单元在<span class=\"name name-commodity\">防御系统</span>和<span class=\"name name-commodity\">危险防护系统</span>中有广泛的应用。<br> <br>可由<span class=\"name name-earth\">铁氧体粉末</span>和地下开采出的<span class=\"name name-technology\">钴</span>化合后制得。经常能在圆柱形金属容器中找到成品。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "方便使用的最佳化能量儲存單元。廣泛用於<span class=\"name name-commodity\">防禦</span>與<span class=\"name name-commodity\">風險防護</span>系統。<br> <br>能融合<span class=\"name name-earth\">鐵氧體粉塵</span>與地下<span class=\"name name-technology\">鈷</span>製成。現成品常見於圓筒形金屬容器中。"
  },
